Subject:[bcp] Ride to the Adopt-a-Highway Road Clean-up on Sunday
Sun November 4, 2012 - Ride to the Adopt-A-Highway Cleanup.
Level C to B-, 12.5-15 mph, 40 miles. Meet at Ft. Washington State Park, Fl=
ourtown Picnic Area. The ride leaves at 9:00 am. Join us getting in some mi=
les AND performing a civic duty (BCP is an Adopt-A-Highway sponsor for a st=
retch of Yellow Springs Rd outside of Valley Forge Nat'l Park). Quick bathr=
oom break at Betzwood picnic area at VFNP before starting the clean-up (wil=
l be less than an hour) and a quick bathroom break at the Valley Forge Visi=
tor Center on the return. Refreshments, snacks, gloves, vests and bags will=
